{"type": "article", "id": 2510, "title": "自行车坐垫锁", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-23T08:14:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1051, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232533vn2kKQLxCBJ8obIi.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>骑行侠们终于可以甩掉麻烦的链条锁了。创业公司 SEATYLOCK 日前在 Kickstarter 上推出了一款集自行车坐垫和车锁于一身的产品，让小偷们再也无处下手！通过在传统自行车坐垫底部增加一个可折叠的连接结构就完成了一举两得的巧思，拆卸十分方便，同时拥有两种不同宽度的尺寸。售价 85 美元，</span><a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/seatylock/seatylock-bicycle-saddle-and-lock-in-one-amazing-p\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里预定。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052325317IQXK3NA8wY6gBPH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232531BcGsp81UVo9hDzPL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232532cDkZ8XEM47OjozPa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232532uzfT7HIEgrF3V1SC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.309375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}